<br>
His unearthly new white eyes scanned the empty streets with grim determination. Soon this must end. Innoruuk's Will must be done.<br>
<br>
He walked past the older Manses of the Noble families as he made his way back to House S`Therik, and paused as he came upon House D`Plith. Light glowed from behind every window, though the facade of the House remained dark and forboding. He arched an eyebrow as he considered the meaning of this. The Vicar Yathrin had stood beside the Violent Harvest once, if only for a brief time. Had Innoruuk returned her to Norrath then? Why.. and why now? How would this ancient power play in to the Blood Harvest, if at all?<br>
<br>
Slowly he returned to his own House to pray and prepare. Much was left to be done, and there was less time in which to do it.<br>
